# Template Marketplace — <%= appName %>

Search, install, and publish reusable project templates.

## Visibility

| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `public` | Shared catalog templates |
| `private` | Project-local catalog |
| `organization` | Company-scoped templates |

