## CLI

```bash
my template setup
my template search api
my template install api-crud
my template publish ./my-template --visibility private
```

## Usage

```ts
import { registerTemplateMarketplace } from './src/template-marketplace/index.js';

const marketplace = registerTemplateMarketplace();
const { templates } = await marketplace.search('auth');
```
